==家庭==
[[File:Oliver_Stone_and_his_wife_in_Closing_ceremony_of_the_2018_Fajr_International_Film_Festival_09_(cropped).jpg|缩略图]]
史東曾結過三次婚。

*1971年5月22日，與納瓦·薩基斯（Najwa Sarkis）結婚。1977年離婚。
*1981年6月7日，與伊莉莎白·伯基·考克斯（Elizabeth Burkit Cox）結婚<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AZSG19XFvwIC&q=%22OLIVER+STONE%22+ELIZABETH&pg=PR8 |title=''Oliver Stone: Interviews'' |isbn=9781578063031 |last1=Stone |first1=Oliver |year=2001 |access-date=2021-01-24 |archive-date=2021-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211115171332/https://books.google.com/books?id=AZSG19XFvwIC&q=%22OLIVER+STONE%22+ELIZABETH&pg=PR8 }}</ref>。育有兩名兒子：[[西恩·史東|西恩]]<ref>{{Cite news|title=EXCLUSIVE: He sat on Michael Douglas' lap and co-starred with Kevin Costner in JFK but Sean Stone - son of director Oliver Stone – says getting his first kiss in the back of an Olds while playing Jim Morrison in hit movie was the best|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5845091/Oliver-Stones-son-Sean-reveals-like-growing-famous-director-father.html|accessdate=2021-01-08|date=2018-06-15|last=West|first=Ryan Parry|work=Mail Online|language=en|archive-date=2018-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616025301/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5845091/Oliver-Stones-son-Sean-reveals-like-growing-famous-director-father.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>（1984年生）和麥可（1991年生）。這段婚姻最後仍以離婚告終。
* 1996年，與Sun-jung Jung結婚。育有一名女兒塔拉（1995年生）。

